OL,5, A 15-year-old black schoolgirl         
OL,6, strip-searched by police was pulled out
OL,7, of an exam so the "traumatic incident" 
OL,8, could take place, a safeguarding report
OL,9, says.                                  
OL,11,FTeachers at her Hackney school called  
OL,12,Fthe Met Police after wrongly suspecting
OL,13,Fher of carrying cannabis in 2020.      
OL,15,FThe report found the search, without   
OL,16,Fanother adult present, was unjustified 
OL,17,Fand racism "likely" a factor. Local MP 
OL,18,FDiane Abbott also said it was racist.  
OL,20,FScotland Yard said the search "should  
OL,21,Fnever have happened".                  
